{"name":"Experienced Crook","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"any alignment","hitDice":"7","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (splint)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"38 (7d8 + 7)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"13","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The veteran can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The veteran regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the veteran can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the veteran can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The veteran can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the veteran's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the veteran's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the veteran dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Tripping Attack (1day)","desc":"When the [MON] hits with a melee attack, they can deal an extra 1d8 damage and the target has to make a [DEX SAVE] dexterity save or fall prone."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two Shortsword attacks."},{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] piercing damage."},{"name":"Light Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D8] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Nimble Escape","desc":"The [MON] can take the Disengage or Hide action as a bonus action on each of its turns."},{"name":"Parry","desc":"The [MON] adds 2 to its AC against one melee attack that would hit it. To do so, the [MON] must see the attacker and be wielding a melee weapon."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Parry","desc":"The [MON] adds 2 to its AC against one melee attack that would hit it. To do so, the [MON] must see the attacker and be wielding a melee weapon."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"sleight of Hand","stat":"dex"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Crook","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}